class Solution {
    public long waysToBuyPensPencils(int total, int cost1, int cost2) {
        long ways = 0;
        for (int pens = 0; pens <= total / cost1; pens++) {
            for (int pencils = 0; pencils <= (total - pens * cost1) / cost2; pencils++) {
                if (pens * cost1 + pencils * cost2 <= total) {
                    ways++;
                }
            }
        }
        return ways;
    }
}
```
efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(total/cost1 * total/cost2)
space complexity: O(1)
energy implications: LOW
